  • Package burlap.mdp.singleagent.common

    • Class burlap.mdp.singleagent.common.VisualActionObserver extends JFrame implements Serializable

      serialVersionUID:
      1L

      • Serialized Fields

        • domain

          OODomain domain
          The domain this visualizer is rendering

        • painter

          Visualizer painter
          The visualizer that will render states

        • propViewer

          TextArea propViewer
          Text area to display the propositional functions that are true

        • cWidth

          int cWidth
          The width of the painter

        • cHeight

          int cHeight
          The height of the painter

        • actionRenderDelay

          long actionRenderDelay
          How long to wait in ms for a state to be rendered before returning control to the agent. Default is 17ms (about 60fps)

        • repaintStateOnEnvironmentInteraction

          boolean repaintStateOnEnvironmentInteraction
          If true (which is default), then the post-state in an VisualActionObserver.observeEnvironmentInteraction(burlap.mdp.singleagent.environment.EnvironmentOutcome) is rendered.

        • repaintOnActionInitiation

          boolean repaintOnActionInitiation
          If true, then a a state-action pair is rendered on calls to VisualActionObserver.observeEnvironmentActionInitiation(State, Action) so long as the input Visualizer has a set StateActionRenderLayer. Default value is false.
